        "text": "2 Chronicles 2:7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), with the signification, \"and let there be prepared for me\" (Berth.). It is subordinated to the preceding clauses: send me cedars, which thy people who are skilful in the matter hew, and in that my servants will assist, in order, viz., to prepare me building timber in plenty (the ו is explic). On ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
