        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 5:10",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; see on ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 2:14",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". להטבים is more closely defined by העצים לכרתי, and ל is the introductory ל: \"and behold, as to the hewers, the fellers of trees.\" חטב, to hew (wood), and to dress it (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Deuteronomy 29:10",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Joshua 9:21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
