        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), would seem to have been supplanted by חצב, which in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 2:2",
        "children": []
      },
      {
